=========================
Features
=========================

This allows people to transfer ownership of groups to their friends.
You can find the transfer option in the edit window of a group. 
You can only transfer to your friends, and they will automatically become a member of the group (duh).
Plugin setting allow you to choose who can transfer ownership (siteadmin and groupadmin)

